, 
<emphasis id="B912EAD2FFE9FFD2FB30FAD3CBD3FAB5" box="[1156,1253,1339,1364]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">P. s k u l e i</emphasis>
<emphasis id="B912EAD2FFE9FFD2FB41FAD2CA61FAB5" bold="true" box="[1269,1367,1338,1364]" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">sp. nov.</emphasis>
from 
<collectingCountry id="F3717650FFE9FFD2FF23FA8ACFDBFA9D" box="[151,237,1378,1404]" name="Greece" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">Greece</collectingCountry>
, and an undescribed species known by a single female from 
<collectingCountry id="F3717650FFE9FFD2FC64FA8ACB15FA9D" box="[976,1059,1378,1404]" name="Turkey" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">Turkey</collectingCountry>
(aff. 
